snippet.title: The Conjuring: Last Rites | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Discover why this case ended it all. #TheConjuring: Last Rites - Only in Theaters September 5.

From New Line Cinema comes the ninth entry in the more than $2 billion theatrical Conjuring universe, The Conjuring: Last Rites, directed by franchise veteran Michael Chaves and produced by franchise architects James Wan and Peter Safran.

The Conjuring: Last Rites delivers another thrilling chapter of the iconic Conjuring cinematic universe, based on real events.  Vera Farmiga and Patrick Wilson reunite for one last case as renowned, real-life paranormal investigators Ed and Lorraine Warren in a powerful and spine-chilling addition to the global box office-breaking franchise.

Farmiga and Wilson star alongside Mia Tomlinson and Ben Hardy, who portray Ed and Lorraine‚Äôs daughter Judy Warren and her boyfriend, Tony Spera, as well as Steve Coulter returning as Father Gordon, Rebecca Calder, Elliot Cowan, K√≠la Lord Cassidy, Beau Gadsdon, John Brotherton and Shannon Kook.

Chaves directs from a screenplay by Ian Goldberg & Richard Naing and David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick, story by David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick & James Wan, based on characters created by Chad Hayes & Carey W. Hayes.  The executive producers are Michael Clear, Judson Scott, Hans Ritter, David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick, Natalia Safran, John Rickard and Michael Chaves.

Chaves is joined behind the camera by his creative team, including director of photography Eli Born, production designer John Frankish, editors Elliot Greenberg and Gregory Plotkin, visual effects supervisor Scott Edelstein, visual effects producer Eric Bruneau and costume designer Graham Churchyard, with casting by Rose Wicksteed and Sophie Kingston-Smith.  The music supervisor is Ian Broucek and the music is by composer Benjamin Wallfisch.

New Line Cinema Presents The Safran Company / An Atomic Monster Production, The Conjuring: Last Rites.  The film will be released worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures and will be only in theaters and IMAX¬Æ in North America on September 5, 2025, and internationally beginning 3 September 2025.

snippet.title: Mortal Kombat: Legacy Kollection - Official Physical Edition Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the latest Mortal Kombat: Legacy Kollection trailer for the fighting game compilation to see the announcement from Digital Eclipse and Atari that physical editions are coming, as revealed during EVO 2025. Physical editions of Mortal Kombat: Legacy Kollection will include Standard, Deluxe, and Kollector‚Äôs Editions. Additionally, Mortal Kombat: Legacy Kollection will also include the return of Mortal Kombat Trilogy, the 1996 entry that brought every playable character from the 2D Mortal Kombat series into one single game.

snippet.title: Monster Hunter Stories 3: Twisted Reflection - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
A new tale of Riders and monsters takes flight! Monster Hunter Stories 3: Twisted Reflection, the next evolution of the turn-based, story-rich RPG series, is coming to Nintendo Switch 2, PS5, Xbox Series X|S, and PC/Steam in 2026. 

Twin Rathalos, born in a twist of fate, ignite the long dormant flames of war between two fractured nations: Azuria and Vermeil. You are the heir to the kingdom of Azuria, and the sole Rathalos Rider in the kingdom. On the brink of war and amidst strange phenomena threatening the world, a life changing event propels you beyond the Meridian, and on an unforgettable journey in search of the truth. 

Learn more:
https://www.monsterhunter.com/stories3/

snippet.title: Dax - "Man I Used To Be" (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
[LYRICS BELOW] "Man I Used To Be" is a personal song i wrote. Share this with everyone and anyone and let's make an impact. Somebody out there needs this. Love y'all...Thank you.

Click here to listen:  https://dax.lnk.to/TheManIUsedToBe


Follow DAX: @ thatsdax
Shot by: Logan Meis
Produced by: Jimmy Robbins


#ManIUsedToBe #Dax #recovery #masculinity #addiction #sober #manhood


LYRICS:

I‚Äôm half the man I used to be 
It‚Äôs gon‚Äô take some getting used to me
I used to think I had it all
But when you‚Äôre up all you do is fall
And that‚Äôs why I‚Äôm
Half the man I used to be

Trials and tribulations 
All my past trauma
Generational curses from daddy and mama
Heartbreak and lies
Dirty soul ties 
Mixed with addictions that clouded my eyes
I‚Äôve been mistaken and taken for granted
and locked in the prison that I call my mind
And now that I‚Äôve lived and I‚Äôve learned  
And I‚Äôve built and I‚Äôve burned all these bridges I‚Äôll leave it behind
And that‚Äôs why

I‚Äôm half the man I used to be 
It‚Äôs gon‚Äô take some getting used to me
I used to think I had it all
But when you‚Äôre up all you do is fall
And that‚Äôs why I‚Äôm
Half the man I used to be

Don‚Äôt ask the reason I changed
Ask yourself why you stayed the same 
I couldn‚Äôt sleep in that bed I made
I needed more in life 
I tried every remedy prescribed 
Getting drunk every night 
Letting women waste my time 
Now I‚Äôm in a phase I can sleep alone 
I don‚Äôt ever chase, I got God
Letting go of pain that was never mine
Trying to bear the weights 
not my job 
Cause that‚Äôs the man i used to be
And he ain't no use to me

I‚Äôm half the man I used to be 
It‚Äôs gon‚Äô take some getting used to me
I used to think I had it all
But when you‚Äôre up all you do is fall
And that‚Äôs why I‚Äôm
Half the man I used to be

I‚Äôm half the man I used to be 
It‚Äôs gon‚Äô take some getting used to me
I used to think I had it all
But when you‚Äôre up all you do is fall
And that‚Äôs why I‚Äôm
Half the man I used to be

______________________________________________________

If you made it this deep you're a real one. Thank you for continuing to allow me to use my platform to make an impact. Your support is appreciated more than you'll ever know and I will continue to prove that with my actions. I'm very excited. This is our first new release of 2025 and the first song I've ever released under complete prolonged clarity. This year will have my best and most impactful work. I am putting everything into creating pieces we can all be proud of. This is music for the PEOPLE, spread BY THE PEOPLE. Like, comment, SHARE and let's continue to be the change we wish to see in the world.

snippet.title: GOAT - Official Teaser Trailer (HD)
snippet.description:
You‚Äôre never too small to dream big.

From the studio that brought you Spider-Man: Across the #SpiderVerse and producer Stephen Curry, #GOATmovie is exclusively in movie theatres February 2026.

Visit our site: https://goat.movie/
Find your team: https://theroarleague.com/

Follow Us on Social:
https://www.instagram.com/goatmovieofficial
https://www.facebook.com/goatmovieofficial

Subscribe for more exclusive content: https://www.youtube.com/@sonypictures

From Sony Pictures Animation, the studio behind Spider-Man: Across the Spider-Verse, comes GOAT, an original action-comedy set in an all-animal world. The story follows Will, a small goat with big dreams who gets a once-in-a-lifetime shot to join the pros and play roarball ‚Äì a high-intensity, co-ed, full-contact sport dominated by the fastest, fiercest animals in the world. Will‚Äôs new teammates aren‚Äôt thrilled about having a little goat on their roster, but Will is determined to revolutionize the sport and prove once and for all that ‚Äúsmalls can ball!‚Äù

Directed by: Tyree Dillihay

snippet.title: This Roblox Scammer Promised to Quit, So I Stalked Him...
snippet.description:
...and it turns out I found him doing something even worse.

ElijahGives is infamously known as Roblox's most desperate scammer, and he told me he was going to quit. So after Elijah promised me to stop scamming kids on roblox, I secretly stalked him and figured out his previous scams and cybercrimes he committed in the past.

And while I thought he gave up scamming because he got relentlessly cyberbullied for being a pathetic scammer, it turns out Elijah's dark past caught up to him and caused even more problems.


SOCIALS
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Discord Server
https://discord.gg/ntts

Twitter
https://twitter.com/notexttospeech

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji. ‚ÄúAlpha‚Äù, the seventh instalment in the franchise and Hindi cinema's first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, is set to release on 25 December 2025.

snippet.title: THIS IS NOT SKYRIM 2 - BECOMING A GOD In Tainted Grail A PERFECTLY BALANCED GAME
snippet.description:
What Does It Take To Make A God In A Video Game.

The year is 2025 and with bethesda teasing a return to the world of oblivion gamers are once again searching for a taste of skyrim. With the oblivion remaster looking to be a remake that fleshes out some skyrim systems like stealth archer builds I thought it would be a good idea to dive into a new games spin on the RPG formula. This game is Tainted Grail: The Fall of Avalon. It has split news outlets with half saying it is an indie skyrim and half saying its indie dark souls. For me the spiffing brit this game is perfectly balanced. Remember this game is NOT SKYRIM but perhaps just like skyrim we can find infinite money glitches, overpowered magic and an array of silly physics moments. 

If you are interested in the game you can grab it on steam sale here at some point: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1466060/Tainted_Grail_The_Fall_of_Avalon/

It is described as follows: Step into a dark reimagination of Arthurian legends in this first person, open world RPG. Explore a world stuck in everlasting autumn, witness falling legends and make meaningful choices woven into a complex, branching storyline. SO yeah it does indeed hit all of the lovely buzzwords that todd howard used to draw me into the world of tamriel and skyrim all those years ago. So lets hunt for bugs, glitches and exploits in this open world adventure.

en-GB.title: THIS IS NOT SKYRIM 2 - BECOMING A GOD In Tainted Grail A PERFECTLY BALANCED GAME
en-GB.description:
What Does It Take To Make A God In A Video Game.

The year is 2025 and with bethesda teasing a return to the world of oblivion gamers are once again searching for a taste of skyrim. With the oblivion remaster looking to be a remake that fleshes out some skyrim systems like stealth archer builds I thought it would be a good idea to dive into a new games spin on the RPG formula. This game is Tainted Grail: The Fall of Avalon. It has split news outlets with half saying it is an indie skyrim and half saying its indie dark souls. For me the spiffing brit this game is perfectly balanced. Remember this game is NOT SKYRIM but perhaps just like skyrim we can find infinite money glitches, overpowered magic and an array of silly physics moments. 

If you are interested in the game you can grab it on steam sale here at some point: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1466060/Tainted_Grail_The_Fall_of_Avalon/

It is described as follows: Step into a dark reimagination of Arthurian legends in this first person, open world RPG. Explore a world stuck in everlasting autumn, witness falling legends and make meaningful choices woven into a complex, branching storyline. SO yeah it does indeed hit all of the lovely buzzwords that todd howard used to draw me into the world of tamriel and skyrim all those years ago. So lets hunt for bugs, glitches and exploits in this open world adventure.

snippet.title: Blade: The One and Only | Character Reveal | Marvel Rivals
snippet.description:
üßõ Half human, half vampire, you know his name ‚Äî Blade. 
 
Almost a century ago, Eric Brooks was born of two worlds: the light of his mother's embrace and the dark of the vampire that attacked her. After embracing his existence as a dhampir, he became the Daywalker, the ultimate vampire hunter, combining unmatched combat skills and unwavering supernatural abilities. 
 
When Dracula reigned over New York City, it was none other than Blade who confronted him first. By then, however, it was too late. Dracula had mastered the almighty power of Chronovium, defeating the Daywalker and imprisoning him within the castle dungeon. 
 
After Dracula's fall, Blade was sent to Wakanda to recover, but his story is far from over. Now recruited by Shuri to save all existence, Blade stands awake and at the ready against the dark forces of Hela and Knull.
 
Only time will tell how this will all unfold, find out more about S3.5 on August 8 UTC. üó°Ô∏è

On this channel, I discuss topics like RPGs, CRPGs, JRPGs, FFXIV, Baldur's Gate 3, Diablo 4, Path of Exile, Elden Ring, MMOs, World of Warcraft, and gaming industry news.

‚ÄúThe End Continues‚Äù is the newest album from Spinal Tap, in conjunction with the forthcoming sequel, ‚ÄòSpinal Tap II: The End Continues.‚Äô Both the second film and album are set to release on September 12, 2025. snippet.title: I Built 4 Animal Bases in 99 Nights in the Forest!
snippet.description:
I trapped every wild animal inside my forest base... and turned it into a zoo (or maybe a prison). Each animal got their own enclosure ‚Äî a bear, wolf, polar bear, and even a bunny. (The deer was a bit of a challenge, you have to see what happens lol)

Will they escape? Probably.

snippet.title: Starve Away!
snippet.description:
god-sanctioned death
the kind that I like best
I like a good just war
it's what guns are for
I like a good crusade
it brightens my day
starve away!

annihilate
with cosmic vindication
bring us John Wayne justice
for the chosen nation
lord, scatter their bones in your sweetness
speed forth the second coming of the great white Jesus

this is my prayer unto you
oh lord, I hope it comes true
rain down your blessings from heaven on me
and starve the women and the children of my enemy

warranted pain
and holy retribution
couple things my god needs
to make a solution
may their children wander aimless in desolated streets
with no memory of a mother, no father indeed

raised up by war
their fist in a clench
breed the next generation
of bombs in the ditch

this is my prayer unto you
oh lord I hope it comes true
rain down your blessings from heaven on my
and starve the women and the children of my enemy

my congressman's 
got a heavy load on his back
it's full of money and blood
str8 outa a pack
he's in the tall cotton
but he hasn't forgotten
to starve away

my guvner
buys his rarely bonds
with the taxes of the poor
down in Arkansas
she says lucky me
i'ma huckabee
starve away

this is my prayer unto you
oh lord I hope it comes true
rain down your blessings from heaven on my
and starve the women and the children of my enemy

snippet.title: Edge of Fate's fate was already sealed. (First Impressions)
snippet.description:
my first impressions on edge of fate are here. it's not a perfect expansion, not even close. i have my fair share of gripes about the campaign gameplay and about leveling. new foundations are being formed, plenty of new systems to tweak to get them right. but it felt like a lot of people went into the expansion hating it before it even came out and i do think the hate has gone a bit too far.

i plan on using this space to give more thoughts as i get questions/topics to discuss. if i get enough things that i wanna follow up on, i'll just make another video.

story - 0:26
campaign gameplay - 6:56
the portal/leveling - 13:59
stat revamps/new gear - 26:05
ultimately though - 31:28

snippet.title: Thanks Nintendo
snippet.description:
Nintendo just made another update patch with HUGE consequences for MKWorld. According to the patch notes, "lap-type" courses will show up more online instead of "intermission" (or route or highway) tracks. But is that really true? And why did they change how trick boosts work?

How to do all the best shortcuts: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XFJmt_LEUa0
How to play regular tracks online: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eLIt4s7NKM0

11:10 IMPORTANT: Trick Boost Change

snippet.title: We're On Fire With Slot Bonuses! Ft. Bluff
snippet.description:
We're back with @Bluffinbob firing at the Casino, seeing if we can get a huge win for the vlog.  We've got baccarat, we've got slots, we've got even more slots, and some roulette too.  It's time to see if we can get a massive hand pay.  Thank you all so much for liking, subscribing, and dropping your thoughts in the comments. Even if you‚Äôre roasting me‚ÄîI still love you. You‚Äôre all beautiful, and I truly appreciate every single one of you for riding along on this crazy journey.  Wish me luck, and I‚Äôll see you in the next one! Let‚Äôs go to war.

Brettski and Bluff walked through the casino doors like outlaws entering a saloon. The plan was simple: start with $10,000, play smart, and maybe‚Äîjust maybe‚Äîwalk out legends.

They hit the high-limit room first. Brettski sat at a $100 blackjack table, Bluff drifted toward the slots, eyes locked on a glimmering machine called Dragon's Vault. Within minutes, Brettski caught fire‚Äîblackjack after blackjack. He stacked chips so high, even the pit boss raised an eyebrow. Bluff, meanwhile, hit a mini jackpot on his third spin: $4,200. They met back up, high-fived, and doubled down.

Feeling invincible, Brettski suggested roulette. Bluff grinned. ‚ÄúLet‚Äôs go red until we can‚Äôt feel feelings.‚Äù They threw $5,000 on red. Ball spun. Landed on green. A gasp. The air changed. Bluff laughed, but it sounded hollow.

Chasing the loss, they found a progressive slot near the cashier cage called Pharaoh‚Äôs Curse. Jackpot over a million. Bluff said, ‚ÄúThis is it.‚Äù They pooled the last of their winnings: $6,700 into one final push.

Spin after spin, nothing. Then, on a random $125 bet, the reels lit up. Bonus round. Brettski and Bluff held their breath. The screen flashed: ‚ÄúEnter the Tomb for a chance at the Grand Prize.‚Äù A pyramid appeared. Three doors.

‚ÄúPick one,‚Äù Bluff whispered.

Brettski hovered over the screen‚Ä¶ picked the middle door.

The animation dragged. Smoke. Symbols. A golden sarcophagus opened‚Äî

Suddenly, the machine froze.

Lights dimmed. Alarms rang. Not jackpot alarms‚Äîsecurity alarms.

A voice came over the loudspeaker: ‚ÄúAttention guests, please remain where you are. The casino is on temporary lockdown.‚Äù

Brettski turned to Bluff. ‚ÄúWhat the hell is happening?‚Äù

Bluff stared at the frozen screen.

And then, out of nowhere, the machine whispered a single word:

‚ÄúRun.‚Äù

Brettski's goal as a Professional Gambler is simple: own all of Las Vegas, using funds made by Gambling.  Subscribe to support his journey in world domination.

We hebben baccarat, gokkasten, nog meer gokkasten en ook nog wat roulette. Het is tijd om te kijken of we een flinke hand kunnen winnen. Heel erg bedankt allemaal voor het liken, abonneren en het achterlaten van jullie mening in de reacties. Zelfs als jullie me belachelijk maken, hou ik nog steeds van jullie. Jullie zijn allemaal prachtig, en ik waardeer het enorm dat jullie allemaal mee hebben gedaan aan deze waanzinnige reis. Wens me succes en ik zie jullie in de volgende! Laten we ten strijde trekken.

Brettski en Bluff liepen door de casinodeuren als criminelen die een saloon binnengaan. Het plan was simpel: beginnen met $10.000, slim spelen en misschien ‚Äì heel misschien ‚Äì als legendes naar buiten komen.

Ze gaan als eerste naar de high-limit room. Brettski zat aan een blackjacktafel van $100, Bluff dwaalde naar de gokkasten, zijn ogen gericht op een glinsterende machine genaamd Dragon's Vault. Binnen enkele minuten vatte Brettski vuur ‚Äì blackjack na blackjack. Hij stapelde zo hoog dat zelfs de pitboss een wenkbrauw optrok. Bluff won ondertussen een minijackpot bij zijn derde draai: $4200. Ze ontmoetten elkaar weer, gaven elkaar een high five en verdubbelden.

Zich onoverwinnelijk voelend, stelde Brettski roulette voor. Bluff grijnsde. "Laten we rood spelen tot we geen gevoelens meer kunnen voelen." Ze gooiden $5000 op rood. De bal draaide. Landde op groen. Een zucht. De lucht veranderde. Bluff lachte, maar het klonk hol.

Op zoek naar hun verlies vonden ze een progressieve gokkast vlak bij de kassa, genaamd Pharaoh's Curse. Jackpot meer dan een miljoen. Bluff zei: "Dit is hem." Ze legden hun laatste winst: $ 6.700 in √©√©n laatste poging.

Spin na spin, niets. Toen, met een willekeurige inzet van $ 125, lichtten de rollen op. Bonusronde. Brettski en Bluff hielden hun adem in. Het scherm flitste: "Betreed de Tombe voor een kans op de Hoofdprijs." Er verscheen een piramide. Drie deuren.

"Kies er √©√©n," fluisterde Bluff.

Brettski zweefde boven het scherm... koos de middelste deur.

De animatie sleepte. Rook. Symbolen. Een gouden sarcofaag ging open‚Äî

Plotseling bevroor de machine.

De lichten dimden. Alarmen gingen af. Geen jackpotalarmen, maar beveiligingsalarmen.

Een stem klonk door de luidspreker: "Attentie gasten, blijf alstublieft waar u bent. Het casino is tijdelijk afgesloten."

Brettski draaide zich om naar Bluff. "Wat is er in vredesnaam aan de hand?"

Bluff staarde naar het bevroren scherm.

En toen, uit het niets, fluisterde de machine een enkel woord:

"Rennen."

Una voce risuon√≤ dall'altoparlante: "Attenzione ospiti, siete pregati di rimanere dove siete. Il casin√≤ √® temporaneamente chiuso".

Brettski si rivolse a Bluff. "Che diavolo sta succedendo?"

snippet.title: Past Life #4 - Improv is a Blast!
snippet.description:
Past Life is an odd mix of a Social and PvP Minecraft game started by Grian. Players are thrown into a tiny world with almost no rules, except survive as long as possible.

In Past Life, we will be playing through the older versions of Minecraft and updating to a newer one each episode.

3+ Lives = Green Player
2 Lives = Yellow Player
1 Life = Red Player

Red Players are given the goal of killing all the other players in the game. Yellow Players can kill Green Players.
